Patch 6.1.032
Problem:    Can't specify a quickfix file without jumping to the first error.
Solution:   Add the ":cgetfile" command. (Yegappan Lakshmanan)
Files:	    runtime/doc/index.txt, runtime/doc/quickfix.txt, src/ex_cmds.h,
	    src/quickfix.c

