--- 101,111 ----
  			keep Vim running while compiling.  If you give the
  			name of the errorfile, the 'errorfile' option will
  			be set to [errorfile].  See |:cc| for [!].
+ 
+ 							*:cg* *:cgetfile*
+ :cg[etfile][!] [errorfile]
+ 			Read the error file.  Just like ":cfile" but don't
+ 			jump to the first error.
  
  							*:cl* *:clist*
  :cl[ist] [from] [, [to]]
